110
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,199
Jadi maksud awak

111
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,600
saya hanya mengalahkan orang bodoh?

112
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,319
Bukan itu maksud saya.

113
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,279
