114
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,920
saya tersalah faham keadaan?

115
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,879
Bahawa saya tak fikir akibat kalah?

116
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,319
Maafkan saya.

117
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,639
Saya tersilap cakap.

118
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:39,759
Atau awak fikir

119
